<p><span style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;">What is Cash Renegade?</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 13px;">I believe that Affiliate marketing is really a numbers game.  You should not expect to make a large amount of money from one site especially if you are  are targetting low competition niches which usually have lower traffic and are less lucrative.  That&#8217;s where Cash Renegade comes into the picture. Cash Renegade is software that generates websites so you can create numerous websites easily. </span><span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 13px;">The other fantastic feature of Cash Renegade is that it is designed to give these sites traffic.</span></h2>
